  "text": "MORTALITY -In a German epidemiological cohort study, which involved 3,268 patients with type 2 diabetes followed for a mean follow-up of 6.5 years, investigating the relationship of SMBG with disease-related morbidity and mortality, the total rate of fatal and nonfatal events was lower in SMBG patients than in non-SMBG patients [CITATION_1] .",
